"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-30-team-gb-star-fumes-drink-hot-water-olympics-exit-21328314\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Jack Draperwas left unimpressed after tennis stars at theOlympicshad no choice but to drink 'hot water' in the sweltering heat ofParis.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 4, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9983174404400099, \"rank\": 0.001321035402742287, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team GB star's Olympics campaign came to an end on Tuesday after he was knocked out of the men's singles.\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The British No.1 won the first set against seventh seed Taylor Fritz on the tiebreak, but the American was in control afterward, winning the remaining sets, 6-3, 6-2.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 252, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9976211145462898, \"rank\": 0.0008411031294501395, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taylor Fritz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\"}, {\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999511482556328, \"rank\": 4.589717559561542e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like many others, Draper struggled to cope with the scorching conditions at Roland Garros, with temperatures hitting at least 36 degree celsius in the French capital.\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.5980802104080393, \"rank\": 0.6482664317211191, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow\\u00a0Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  The 22-year-old acknowledged it was all part of the game, but also hit out at organisers after he was unable to keep his water cool, saying: 'It was tough conditions, there is no doubt about it.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I need to play more in this sort of heat, and obviously, going toAmerica, I will get more used to that.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was really hot out there today.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We were both trying our best to put out some good tennis.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Part of it's physicality but I said to the referee, it's pretty poor that the players have to drink hot water when we are playing in those conditions.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's important we have good fridges to keep our water cool.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so tough to recover when you are just not replenishing properly.'\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of fridges, players have been given refillable bottles and water fountains, with organisers looking to be more environmentally friendly and make Paris 2024 the greenest games in history.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1491, \"end\": 1501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.541822198577927e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is no escape from the heat, even at the change of ends.\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not played in much hotter conditions than that.\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your body starts to really fight against you,' Draper added.\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We should not have to fill our water up every change of ends, we need to sit down.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1797, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not good enough.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just think it's pretty poor that they put the players through that on court.'\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He wasn't the only tennis star left fuming on Tuesday, with the world No.2Coco Gauff left in tearsafter she was shockingly eliminated from the women's singles.\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 2060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The US flagbearer hit out at the umpire for her match, exclaiming: 'I am getting cheated!'\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9990768123356792, \"rank\": 0.0005451959213565579, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Mario & Sonic games cancelled thanks to Olympic Committee reveals source  ArrowMORE:Simone Biles embarrassed after 'forgetting' Olympics protocol in team final  ArrowMORE:BBC Olympics presenter Clare Balding embroiled in 'classism' row after 'privileged' remark  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2457, \"end\": 2460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.7944042480753766, \"rank\": 0.25859405461926266, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 2480, \"end\": 2493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Clare Balding\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2855, \"end\": 2861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202962604, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Som